snippet.title: Anamorphine Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Anamorphine launches July 31, 2018 for PC, VR and PS4 on
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/545620/Anamorphine/ 
PS4: https://www.playstation.com/en-ca/games/anamorphine-ps4/
Humble Store
Green Man Gaming
Nuuvem

Explore the past as you resolve the present in Anamorphine, a surreal adventure of rendered emotions. Journey into the mind of the main character, a young man in denial. His subconscious is pushing him to face his past - or be consumed by it.
